citations:
    citation-agot-eddard-iii:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Eddard III"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Arya's hearing at Castle Darry before King Robert and Cersei. Robert orders Lady (Sansa's direwolf) killed as a stand-in for Nymeria. Ned kills Lady himself rather than let Ilyn Payne do it. Sandor Clegane returns with Mycah's body — the butcher's boy has been cut nearly in half. The castle is Ser Raymun Darry's seat."
